---
import MainGridLayout from "../layouts/MainGridLayout.astro";
---

<MainGridLayout title="友链" description="博客友链与站点信息">
	<div class="grid gap-4">
		<section class="card-base rounded-[var(--radius-large)] px-8 py-7">
			<p class="links-eyebrow">Friends</p>
			<h1 class="links-title">友链</h1>
			<p class="links-copy">
				这里会慢慢收录一起写博客、做题、研究技术的站点。现在先放本站信息和交换说明，后面你有想加的友链可以继续补进来。
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="links-grid">
			<article class="card-base rounded-[var(--radius-large)] px-6 py-6">
				<h2 class="links-card-title">本站信息</h2>
				<div class="links-info">
					<div><span>名称</span><strong>AlF-0v0-blog</strong></div>
					<div><span>地址</span><a href="https://alf-ovo.github.io/alf-ovo-blog/">https://alf-ovo.github.io/alf-ovo-blog/</a></div>
					<div><span>简介</span><strong>CTF-Pwn 相关文章与一些杂谈</strong></div>
					<div><span>头像</span><strong>当前站点头像即可</strong></div>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="card-base rounded-[var(--radius-large)] px-6 py-6">
				<h2 class="links-card-title">交换说明</h2>
				<ul class="links-list">
					<li>优先欢迎个人博客、技术博客、CTF 或安全方向站点。</li>
					<li>站点需要能正常访问，内容长期可见。</li>
					<li>如果你之后想开放交换友链，这里可以再加联系方式或留言入口。</li>
				</ul>
			</article>
		</section>
	</div>
</MainGridLayout>

<style>
	.links-eyebrow {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.9);
	}

	.links-title {
		margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.links-copy {
		margin: 1rem 0 0;
		max-width: 44rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.9);
	}

	.links-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.links-card-title {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.links-info {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.9rem;
	}

	.links-info div {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.3rem;
	}

	.links-info span {
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.9);
	}

	.links-info strong,
	.links-info a {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.94);
		word-break: break-all;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.links-list {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.8rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.9);
	}

	:global(.dark) .links-copy,
	:global(.dark) .links-list {
		color: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.84);
	}

	:global(.dark) .links-info strong,
	:global(.dark) .links-info a {
		color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.94);
	}

	@media (max-width: 820px) {
		.links-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
